             was indicted for <rs id="t18221023-63-off342" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18221023-63-off342" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18221023-63-off342" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18221023-63-cd343" type="crimeDate">9th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18221023-63-off342 t18221023-63-cd343"></join>, one copper, value 10 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18221023-63-victim724" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Morgan
                  <interp inst="t18221023-63-victim724" type="surname" value="Morgan"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18221023-63-victim724" type="given" value="William"></interp>
